{"tid":2273494,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"幪面超人x義士x穿越  有冇興趣？","createTime":"2020-11-05T19:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T14:12:42.000Z","uid":376497,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"70135959703b79f4ad3366e37d576797f802707f","tid":2273494,"uid":376497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T19:25:32.000Z","msg":"諗左個故，已經寫左八個章節，劇情二十字內概括:義士穿越未來中國變幪面起人從零開始抗爭。大家就咁聽會唔會有興趣睇？<br />\n<br />\n有ge 話我得閑修改下就會係度開始連載，冇就費事哂大家時間，我另覓他處搞。"},{"pid":"d7068fd8f4402123facfbb66b74f0f7aaf7ce31b","tid":2273494,"uid":361753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T19:41:41.000Z","msg":"回到過去better"},{"pid":"8920600188a353fee0c85544e46e36bec585f77d","tid":2273494,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T21:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n穿越到香港未來 會唔會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0922f94d1d4437619ce91435a53ef77fb62a8f53","tid":2273494,"uid":351710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T21:11:34.000Z","msg":"po上嚟自然有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20149d96928d9c39de116053c57d0c18550690d","tid":2273494,"uid":66952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T23:55:11.000Z","msg":"不如試下少林功夫x唱歌跳舞"},{"pid":"09b36d5abb5389bef96efa07172e6ad64f0aec70","tid":2273494,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T23:57:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e81226a999decc0fc993d2108cb5a3b2759534ef","tid":2273494,"uid":376497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7068fd8f4402123facfbb66b74f0f7aaf7ce31b","tid":2273494,"uid":361753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T19:41:41.000Z","msg":"回到過去better"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:04:52.000Z","msg":"本身係plan過去，但之後覺得未來ge話設定自由度大D(黑科技任我吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\"